resources.string: Studies have repeatedly warned that using gadgets in the evening affects both the quantity and quality of our sleep. Get a Good Night’s Sleep by Filtering Your Phone’s Blue Light.
Please enable location from settings to see the nearby restaurants.

Digital eye strain is the physical discomfort felt after two or more hours in front of a digital screen and is associated with the close to mid-range distance of digital screens, including desktop and laptop computers, tablets, e-readers and smartphones.
By enabling this, app can notify you about when you should take a break from using the mobile.
